 also when katy perry her biggest pop rival is releasing a new album continue reading the main story we’re interested in your feedback on this page tell us what you think related coverage sales of taylor swift’s ‘’ intensify streaming debate nov   apple gains exclusive streaming deal with taylor swift dec   taylor swift criticism spurs apple to change royalties policy june   related coverage sales of taylor swift’s ‘’ intensify streaming debate nov   apple gains exclusive streaming deal with taylor swift dec   taylor swift criticism spurs apple to change royalties policy june   whats next loading go to home page » site index the new york times